&lt;/h1>
&lt;p>An important function of the human brain is memory. &lt;br>
Humans should use this for learning lessons. &lt;br>
Unfortunately, it&amp;rsquo;s often used to create nostalgic moments in present life. &lt;br>
Life only happens in present, it is neither past nor future. &lt;br>
People love dwelling in the past, being nostalgic. &lt;br>
Why? Because they avoid facing the present and fear the future. &lt;br>
So, finding pleasure is only possible by living in the past.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>